  "text": "Trojans are equipped with a functionality called web-inject [CITATION_1] , that can silently modify a webpage on the infected victim's machine to intercept private credentials such as username, password and even 2 nd factor authentication credentials [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] . Two main features are mostly utilised for web injection by banking Trojans as follow:",
